OL,3,CAsian family 'targeted' in Hartlepool
OL,4,Cdisorder will now leave the town
OL,6,FAn Asian family are planning on
OL,7,Ffleeing their home after having their
OL,8,Fwindows smashed in what they believe
OL,9,Fwas a targeted attack during riots in
OL,10,FHartlepool.
OL,12,FSpeaking anonymously to ITV Tyne Tees,
OL,13,Fone of the family members living in
OL,14,Fthe property said their curtains were
OL,15,Fripped out and their windows were
OL,16,Fsmashed "for no reason".
OL,18,FHe said they were left "terrified"
OL,19,Fafter the incident which saw four
OL,20,Fpeople remain inside his house for
OL,21,Faround 20 to 30 minutes.
