OL,3,CAsian family 'targeted' in Hartlepool
OL,4,Cdisorder will now leave the town
OL,6,FIt happened as unrest broke out in the
OL,7,Ftown on Wednesday (31 July) evening.
OL,8,FIt marked the second night of disorder
OL,9,Fin locations across the UK following
OL,10,Fthe mass stabbing of children at a
OL,11,Fdance class in Southport, Merseyside,
OL,12,Fon Monday.
OL,14,FOn Thursday, the man whose family home
OL,15,Fwas reportedly raided told ITV Tyne
OL,16,FTees: "I'm going to move from here."
OL,18,FHe said he was with his mother at the
OL,19,Ftime of the incident during which she
OL,20,Fhad a panic attack.
